The OpenTTD documentation is stored and edited using this <em>wiki</em>. Feel free to start editing as soon as you feel you can, but '''read the [[en/Wiki/Manual of Style|Manual of Style]] first''', and make any tests in the [[en/Sandbox|Sandbox]].  

Visit the [[en/Archive/Community/Village Pump|village pump]] to discuss any major changes or additions to the documentation, or you can start right in on requests posted in the [[en/Requested Articles|article requests]]. Also:

*Some articles need smaller changes to satisfy our needs, and there is a [[:Category:en/To do|list]] of these.  If you don't feel up to writing full articles then this may be a better place to start. 

*There are also some articles that require more work before they can be called finished, and you can browse them in [[:Category:en/Articles to be expanded|Expand category]]. 

*Finally, there are articles concerning [[:Category:en/Current events|current events]] which will become outdated often - why not check the information in these is still current if you have a spare moment?
